Code
la_recursion &lt;- function(N, A0, alpha, tmax) {
  A_return &lt;- numeric(N+1)  # Create output time series vector.
  # Set current A_t to be A_0
  At &lt;- A0
  A_return[1] &lt;- At
  # Iterate 
  for (t in 1:tmax) {
    # Anext is code for A_{t+1}
    Anext &lt;- At + (alpha * At * (1 - (At/N)))
    A_return[t+1] &lt;- Anext
    At &lt;- Anext
  }
  return (A_return)
}

Coding the legacy-adaptive model
